Cell.Text: [S] What are you doing here, outlander? Your kind isn't welcome.
[S] Welcome, child of Mauloch. Your kin bid you welcome to our stronghold.
I don't understand. What is this place?

[S] This is our stronghold. Here, we are free to live as Mauloch intended, away from the prying eyes of the Nords. | You must have been away from your kind for a long time to forget. Come, rest in the longhouse and everything will come back to you.

[S] This is our stronghold. Here, we are free to live as Mauloch intended, away from the prying eyes of the Nords. | You're not an Orc, or Blood-Kin, so stay out. We don't need a reason to dull our weapons on another trespasser.

Node.Caption: DialogueOrcsGuardTopic01: I'm just a traveler. What is this place?

Cell.Text: [S] Ha ha ha. You'll fit right in here. Come inside. Sit by the fires of the longhouse.
[S] Stay away, outlander. Your first step inside this gate will be your last.

Node.Caption: DialogueOrcsGuardTopic02: I go where I please, Orc.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Hmm... we've heard whispers of an enchanted pair of gauntlets, hidden and protected by dangerous men, beasts, or worse. | They are called the Forgemaster's Fingers. Bring them to us, and we'll gladly make you Blood-Kin to the Orcs.

Node.Caption: DialogueOrcsGuardQuestionsLetInBranchTopic: How can I convince you to let me in?

Cell.Text: You do not remember the Daedric Lord of the Orcs? The keeper of the Sworn Oath and the Bloody Curse? | We live by his code and follow his teachings. Spend some time with the wise woman and you'll remember.
He is the Daedric Lord of the Orcs. The keeper of the Sworn Oath and the Bloody Curse. | We live by his code and follow his teachings. An outlander like you wouldn't understand.

Cell.Text: There are many strongholds throughout Skyrim, each with a tribe of Orcs living under their own chief.

Node.Caption: DialogueOrcsGuardQuestionsStrongholdTopic: Are there other strongholds out there?

Cell.Text: This stronghold is Dushnikh Yal. Home of Burguk, chief of all Orcs in the Reach.
We call our stronghold Makbur, ruled by chief Shammak, descended of the great founders.
This is Mor Khazgur and we live under chief Larak. The rest is our business.
This is Narzulbur, home of chief Mauhulakh, and owners of the Gloombound Mine.

Node.Caption: DialogueOrcsQuestAccept: I'll bring those gauntlets to you.
DialogueOrcsQuestReject: I don't have time for that.
